thread.title_full: Dickmanns Rent a Car evaluado por Patri Pin

author: Patri Pin
title: Patri Pin
text:
Rented a car in teulada for a weekend and I have to say that I will call again.
People at the branch were really kind and friendly, the car I rented was perfectly clean and brand new!
No deposit was charged but the fuel, and it was refunded straight away when rerurned the car.
I'm looking forward to coming back and rent the same car again.
